  scholars and librarians, conductsresearch on available holdings, and
  selectsand prioritizesmaterials for Executive Board consideration,on all
  matters associated with SAOA's core mission ofproviding digitalresources for
  open access.These include, but are not limited to:
</p>

<ul>
